      <title>孟加拉国将于下周起提高政策利率以抑制价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/bangladesh-to-raise-policy-rates-from-next-week-to-fight-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国央行新任行长阿赫桑·曼苏尔 (Ahsan H. Mansur) 表示，该行计划下周将政策利率提高半个百分点，旨在抑制十多年来飙升至最高水平的通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/bangladesh-to-raise-policy-rates-from-next-week-to-fight-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 13:16:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CFRA 的 Stovall 表示，投资者“风险重现”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-22/-risk-is-back-on-for-investors-says-cfra-s-stovall-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[CFRA 首席投资策略师 Sam Stovall 预计美联储将在 9 月份至少降息 25 个基点，并表示投资者感到“小心翼翼地走上冰面”是安全的。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-22/-risk-is-back-on-for-investors-says-cfra-s-stovall-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 13:04:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
